re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a524875dc3d2b301644ffb7b987e7e79cd485669","tid":1221761,"uid":24961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbaf8805d80595f11b2a49de9e02bfde4fd395eb","tid":1221761,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5c2915f240f7eee5d49df41df3933079a4ad21","tid":1221761,"uid":41545,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"8536e4187685e9f1daa7249b700401ab1501a190","tid":1221761,"uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔係反大陸妹架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:59:04.000Z","msg":"反是今時今日肯企出黎支持的<br />\n都沒有反既理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1000e604c54af764692964cabc2048a152e9e3e1","tid":1221761,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:59:27.000Z","msg":"大陸妹好波"},{"pid":"1fc11ce8416e0af614fd12d18e6040567d3dd83a","tid":1221761,"uid":50847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:59:50.000Z","msg":"有冇連登仔整番個打J Whitelist<br />\n撐送中果啲真係狗也不屌"},{"pid":"c334c4f04e2f3d769f31891c0cca6f17df80331e","tid":1221761,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（希望大家廣傳民陣fb呼籲！）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n毋忘年輕人付出，誓撤回逃犯條例！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民陣反送中遊行</span><br />\n日期：6月16日（星期日）<br />\n遊行開始時間：2:30pm<br />\n遊行起點：維多利亞公園<span style=\"color: gold;\">（有可能再加入其他起點同時前進，請留意民陣fb最新消息）</span><br />\n遊行終點：政府總部<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">核心目標：撤回逃犯條例</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民陣三罷反送中集會</span><br />\n日期：6月17日（星期一）<br />\n集會地點：立法會外<br />\n當日行動：三罷（罷工罷市罷課）<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">（留意返星期一嘅三罷集會係未有時間，要等民陣fb睇下佢地點安排）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">核心目標：撤回逃犯條例</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢場仗仲未完，一日未撤回惡法一日都仲有希望，政府宜家打算抄2014年拖字訣消耗民氣，希望大家可以廣傳民陣fb呼籲，最重要係出席遊行，重現一百萬人光景<br />\n<br />\n我地應該要接受香港和理非佔大多數呢個事實，大多數人都唔會衝始終法律後果太重，所以任何願意作出反惡法嘅和理非行動都應該要支持！（所以唔好再話有人企喺橋上面唔去打，上面99%都係和理非，肯出嚟已經好好，好過唔出嚟喺屋企睇電視嘅多多聲）香港人唔可以再比三毛分化，和理非同勇武必須一齊合作，佔大多數嘅和理非請用盡一切合法方法反對逃犯條例，逃犯條例絕對唔可以通過，否則我地同下一代就會生長喺講句說話都要就住就住，擔驚受怕嘅環境之中，大家絕對唔可以比逃犯條例過到<br />\n<br />\n我相信和理非係有佢嘅威力，可以喚起社會更多人關注，叧一方面亦同時爭取緊國際支持向政府施加壓力（eg取消美國香港關係法、各國商會嘅反對）去迫政府撤回逃犯條例。<br />\n<br />\n總之一句講曬：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n兄弟爬山</span><br />\n好重要所以要講三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4394e3c4ad32209c3c58bcef410bf0add0391a","tid":1221761,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"呢條女係我見過最正嘅港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f3874df9584f7f7bed4d522fce97220d6cfbd5","tid":1221761,"uid":82649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我女神<br />\n<br />\n利申絲"},{"pid":"709d19b510436973b6790f20a68f6f9cb51f1f8b","tid":1221761,"uid":144883,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:02:52.000Z","msg":"咪又係典型買兩邊嘅文，<br />\n佢有講撐邊邊咩"},{"pid":"8277da00aef99bb877d37670f1188dbcfd55f708","tid":1221761,"uid":16338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:03:16.000Z","msg":"唯唯令到越黎越多人敢企出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/